Package: Rmonize
Type: Package
Title: Support Retrospective Harmonization of data
Version: 1.0.1.0003
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Guillaume",
             family = "Fabre",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "guijoseph.fabre@gmail.com",
